00:18:34.430 --> 00:18:37.770
But it's quite an interesting
function.

00:18:37.770 --> 00:18:41.140
OK, so what are you
going to take?

00:18:41.140 --> 00:18:42.560
This often happens.

00:18:42.560 --> 00:18:47.550
We have e to the something,
