00:18:56.390 --> 00:19:01.310
x squared over 2, that quantity

00:19:01.310 --> 00:19:03.060
that's sitting up there.

00:19:03.060 --> 00:19:06.980
And then z, the outside
function, is

00:19:06.980 --> 00:19:11.550
